.TH HSH 1 "April 2026" "1.0" "Simple Shell Man Page"
.SH NAME
hsh \- simple UNIX command interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hsh
[command]
.SH DESCRIPTION
hsh is a simple UNIX command line interpreter that executes commands read from the standard input or from a file.
.SH USAGE
Interactive mode:
.br
    $ ./hsh
.br
    ($) /bin/ls
.br
    ($) exit
.br
Non-interactive mode:
.br
    $ echo "/bin/ls" | ./hsh
.SH COMPILATION
gcc -Wall -Werror -Wextra -pedantic -std=gnu89 *.c -o hsh
